node.text:
Have you ever had problems falling asleep? 🥱😳 A year ago I had insomnia and tried every trick in the book to break out from it 😅 What have you tried? 🙈 Thankfully I found @myinsomniacoach and signed up for his 8 week sleep program.

The program uses cognitive behavioral therapy that works. You go to bed at the same time every day and get out of bed at the same time. ⏰ Never stay in bed If you can’t sleep, get up out of bed until you feel sleepy again. 😴

This is easier said than done, so if you have trouble sleeping then I can heartily recommend Insomnia coach☺️

This is not an ad, I am just really happy to share something I found that works!
